Sentencas: The composite electrode of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (LSCF) and Ag was examined as an air electrode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide,fuel cells.
Titulo: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Ag composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Two types of LSCF/Ag composite electrodes were prepared.
Titulo: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Ag composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: One was made by firing the printed sheet of LSCF-GDC (10 mol % Gd2O3 doped CeO2)-Ag powder mixture on the GDC/8 mol % Y2O3 doped zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte, and the other was prepared by firing the LSCF electrode on GDC/YSZ infiltrating a AgNO3 Solution in the pores of the electrode.
Titulo: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Ag composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Ag composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: both cases, the cathode polarization overpotentials were reduced by the addition of Ag into LSFC.
Titulo: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Ag composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The power density of anode support cells with the LSCF electrode was increased from 0.28 W/cm(2) 2 to 0.34 W/cm(2) 2 at 600 degrees C by infiltrating a AgNO3 Solution into the electrode.
Titulo: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-Ag composite cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
